@page "/"

<PageTitle>Cloud Components Demo</PageTitle>

<div class="page-header">
    <h1>Cloud Components Demo</h1>
    <p>
        A focused playground for the <strong>AngryMonkey Cloud Components</strong> library.
        Each page isolates one component so you can interactively explore its parameters and behavior.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">Components covered</h2>
    <p class="card-subtitle">Use the navigation on the left to jump to any component.</p>
    <ul class="checklist">
        <li><strong>Popup</strong> — overlay modal with size variants, header close, click-outside, and back-navigation</li>
        <li><strong>Dialog</strong> — confirmation dialog built on top of Popup with typed button callbacks</li>
        <li><strong>Switch</strong> — tri-state boolean toggle with customizable on/off/none labels</li>
        <li><strong>Tabs</strong> — tab strip with active state driven by a <code>TabItem</code> list</li>
        <li><strong>Progress Bar</strong> — seekable range bar in Flat, Circle, and Disk styles</li>
        <li><strong>Volume Bar</strong> — mutable volume control composing ProgressBar internally</li>
        <li><strong>Date &amp; Time Picker</strong> — inline calendar and time picker with Date, Time, and DateAndTime modes</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">How to use this demo</h2>
    <p class="card-subtitle">
        Every page contains live interactive examples. Controls above each demo let you
        toggle parameters in real-time. An event log beneath each demo records every callback
        fired so you can verify the component behaves correctly.
    </p>
</div>
